messageBody:
As the creator of QSJ Block, I'd be happy for you
to clean up the kerning. If you do, please send me a
copy.

--- amd64_hacker <amd64_hacker@...> wrote:
<Clipped>
> license, I was going to ask if I could submit yours?
> I was going to just clean up QS Block's kerning and
> submit that, but
> yours looks nicer (IMO).
<Clipped>

===========
Never insult anyone by accident.
- Robert A. Heinlein
